<div id="ta196_85" class="block iDevice_content">
<div class="dentro_contenidos" style="display: block;" id="pagina_1">
<p>This task consists of a series of <b>multiple choice</b> questions which will give the student the chance to show their ability to understand the general gist, the main idea or specific information.</p>
<p>Students will listen to a text and answer to seven multiple choice questions, each of them with three options.</p>
<p>Tips:</p>
<ul>
<li>Before you listen, read carefully the questions and pay attention to the main idea so you can focus on it while listening. You have one minute.</li>
<li>If you have time go back and read the alternatives together with the question.</li>
<li>Wait until the speaker has finished to choose the right option.</li>
<li>Listen for the same idea, not for the same words.</li>
</ul>
